---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Exterior Painting in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock' description='Professional exterior painting across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:420px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 56px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Exterior Painting</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Exterior Painting</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.5;">Weather-resistant finishes that protect the fabric of Middlesex and Home Counties properties for years.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The problem</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Exterior paint fails fast when the surface isn't prepared properly.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Paint applied over unprimed render, poorly cleaned masonry, or damp walls doesn't bond. It blisters, peels, and fails inside two years. The prep is where the job is — the painting is straightforward once the surface is right.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">This is particularly true for rendered properties across Middlesex. White-rendered houses look sharp when the paint is fresh and well-maintained — they look neglected when the paint has failed and the render is staining through.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The Hancock approach</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Prepare properly. Specify the right system. Paint it once.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">We clean and prepare the surface, treat any damp or staining, prime where required, and apply the right exterior masonry paint system for the substrate and aspect. Masonry paint, silicone-based renders, limewash on period properties — the system is chosen for the wall, not the other way around.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">We also paint rendered outbuildings, garden walls, garage doors, and timber and UPVC features. One contractor, one price, one visit.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:48px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:260px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px;">Key areas</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;">
        <a href="/areas/ruislip" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Ruislip</a>
        <a href="/areas/watford" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Watford</a>
        <a href="/areas/windsor" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Windsor</a>
        <a href="/areas/gerrards-cross" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Gerrards Cross</a>
        <a href="/areas/ascot" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Ascot</a>
        <a href="/areas" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#E0FAFF;border:1px solid #0C7BA8;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#0C7BA8;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">All 27 areas →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:260px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px;">Related services</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
        <a href="/services/rendering" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span> Rendering</a>
        <a href="/services/sash-window-painting" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span> Sash Window Painting</a>
        <a href="/services/pebble-dashing" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span> Pebble Dashing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get an exterior painting quote.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;">Fixed price. Agreed before work starts. We cover the full Home Counties corridor.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:28px 0 0;">Cancellations less than 48 hours before booking incur a £100 fee.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
